    "description": "<strong>在游戏的序章中，您可以看到完整版的第一阶段、机制横截面、迷你游戏、第一个任务以及游戏玩法本身的介绍</strong>。<br><strong>探索战场并收集武器：</strong><br>战场上只有你一个人，地平线上没有危险。周围有很多武器残骸--剑、盾牌、头盔......抓住这个大好机会，发挥自己的优势！观察周围环境，收集武器，拿走骑士们的盔甲，分类并挑选其中最好的。收集到足够的武器后，前往工坊。请记住，您的推车无法装载您收集到的所有物品<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/1GIF1.gif?t=1757706572\" /></span><br><br><strong> 复原物品:</strong><br>- 拿起锤子！是时候修理这些歪胳膊了。稍微加热一下，选择合适的工具修复剑身。一套可靠的工具正在等着你。使用这些工具还能获得经验，用来提高你的技能，让你的工作更加高效愉快。收拾盔甲上的残局，不要停止修补。你的努力可以修复很多东西。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/95318d881d96f5b3c3d1d9e6b555b3be.poster.avif?t=1757706572\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/95318d881d96f5b3c3d1d9e6b555b3be.webm?t=1757706572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/95318d881d96f5b3c3d1d9e6b555b3be.mp4?t=1757706572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong> 出售您的作品：</strong><br>- 你的所有努力不仅能支持你的战友，还能帮你赚点外快。使用你所拥有的强大技能，帮助你的村庄，保护你的工作室。潜入强化世界，增强人们的能力，赢得战斗的胜利。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/4f943fbff8fd55fbdad54ceff800ed1d.poster.avif?t=1757706572\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/4f943fbff8fd55fbdad54ceff800ed1d.webm?t=1757706572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/4f943fbff8fd55fbdad54ceff800ed1d.mp4?t=1757706572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>解决附加任务中的谜题:</strong><br>如果你对主要任务感到厌倦，你可以根据有趣且令人上瘾的迷你游戏来完成其他任务。打开城堡、射击弩箭等等。积累经验，扩展技能，让您更深入地融入游戏世界。<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/e197dcaaa12c66808fa3ccec121b9b8d.poster.avif?t=1757706572\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/e197dcaaa12c66808fa3ccec121b9b8d.webm?t=1757706572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/e197dcaaa12c66808fa3ccec121b9b8d.mp4?t=1757706572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>探寻王国历史中隐藏的故事:</strong><br>这个世界充满了神秘和阴谋。仔细观察周围，因为有些居民可能需要您的帮助。与他们交谈以获取有价值的信息，或者您将被赋予一项特殊任务。记住，人们总是会为你的帮助支付高昂的报酬！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/1d023cf3c27bbf0b9cc25ec0601b8b57.poster.avif?t=1757706572\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/1d023cf3c27bbf0b9cc25ec0601b8b57.webm?t=1757706572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/1d023cf3c27bbf0b9cc25ec0601b8b57.mp4?t=1757706572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>探索更多城市和战场:</strong> <br>整个王国占地辽阔。其中一些是危险的战场，每天都有数十名骑士牺牲。另一方面，这里也有巨大的商业城市，其惊人的建筑风格令人惊叹。踏上旅程，到达王国最偏远的角落。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/9e177e7feb5cb53485fb9384c1e2703b.poster.avif?t=1757706572\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389150/extras/9e177e7feb5cb53485fb9384c1e2703b.webm?t=1757706572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://sh